* Change the Oracle GitHub job from `docker compose build` to `docker compose up --build -d`.
* Disable/remove the Azure job.
* Verify a new push actually updates running Oracle containers.
* Ensure `.env` and `secrets/` remain server-local and are not removed by `rsync --delete`.
