### P1 — Restart resilience

* Confirm Docker starts on boot.
* Confirm Caddy starts on boot.
* Add suitable Compose restart policies.
* Reboot Oracle in a controlled maintenance window.
* Verify every container returns.
* Verify Caddy still reaches ports 5173 and 3000.
