### P1 — Database migration reliability

* Commit corrected migration `010`.
* Keep migration `011` idempotent.
* Add a migration-state table or migration tool instead of relying only on `/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d`.
* Test initialization against a fresh empty PostgreSQL volume.
* Assert that `app_listening_events_combined` exists.
