### P2 — Resource optimization

The host has one CPU and approximately 6 GB RAM. Consider:

* Limiting concurrent Docker builds.
* Building images in GitHub Actions rather than on the VM.
* Publishing ARM64 images to GHCR.
* Applying memory limits.
* Scheduling large Drive metadata passes during low traffic.
